<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Seni sevaman chin qalbimdan</title>
<aka>Bor qalbim bilan</aka>
<key>F</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
.Dm                C          Gm
 Bor qalbim bilan, bor jonim bilan,
.Dm               C    Gm
 Seni ulugʻlayman Xudoyim.
.Dm                  C       Gm
 Mening bor istagim, bor ibodatim,
.Dm             C       Gm
 Senla boʻlish, Seni sevaman.

[C1]
.         Bb C         Am  Dm
   Seni sevaman bor qalbimdan,
.         Bb C          Am  Dm
   Seni sevaman, mening Rabbimsan.
.        Bb  C     Am   Dm
   Bor hayotim poylaringda,
.  Bb     C            Am   Dm
   Sevgi soʻzlari doim dilimda.

[V2]
 Sen uchun yashayman, Senga kuylayman,
 Har kuni Seni tanib bilaman.
 Oldingda tiz choʻkaman, qalbimni beraman,
 Bor qalbim bilan Seni sevaman.</lyrics>
<author>QURBON MUKUMOV, Irina Repik</author>
</song>